PrecisOrder authorizing the trip to MEXICO made by two Members of Parliament, Mr. PHILIPPE PARÉ (Louis-Hébert) and Mr. ANDREW TELEGDI (Waterloo), from August 17th to August 24th, 1994, to observe the elections as members of the delegation sponsored by the International Centre for Human Rights and Democratic Development.
